WEBVTT

00:00:06.820 --> 00:00:08.620
=Destiny of the General's Bride=

00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:12.020
=Episode 21=

00:00:13.039 --> 00:00:15.359
- Today, we two swear brotherhood.
- Today, we two swear brotherhood.

00:00:15.660 --> 00:00:17.540
- Not seeking to be born the same year,
- Not seeking to be born the same year,

00:00:17.550 --> 00:00:18.750
- same month, same day,
- same month, same day,

00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:20.440
- only wishing to die the same...
- only wishing...

00:00:22.199 --> 00:00:22.879
Wait a moment.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.679
I don't want to die on the same day as you.

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:28.239
You troublemaker.

00:00:28.359 --> 00:00:29.760
Always offending so many people.

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:31.480
If I die with you,

00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:32.840
wouldn't I be losing out?

00:00:33.079 --> 00:00:34.920
I have great fortune,
I won't die easily.

00:00:34.920 --> 00:00:36.119
But letting you die with me

00:00:36.119 --> 00:00:37.880
would be a huge bargain for you.

00:00:44.759 --> 00:00:47.560
Qing Yan really has her tricks.

00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:49.280
They were supposed to fight
like snipe and clam,

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:50.380
letting the fisherman benefit.

00:00:50.560 --> 00:00:51.600
But in the end,

00:00:51.640 --> 00:00:52.920
they became sworn sisters.

00:00:53.420 --> 00:00:56.140
(Xiao Residence)

00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:13.640
Perhaps Xiao Yun
was delayed by official duties.

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:17.560
Forget it, I won't wait for him.

00:01:18.519 --> 00:01:20.719
But there is still one thing

00:01:20.959 --> 00:01:22.120
I cannot set aside.

00:01:24.760 --> 00:01:27.439
After I leave,
you must be wary of Grand Madam Xiao.

00:01:27.799 --> 00:01:29.159
That day when I was kidnapped,

00:01:29.879 --> 00:01:31.840
I seemed to hear her voice.

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:33.079
As if

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:34.680
she wanted your life.

00:01:38.959 --> 00:01:40.290
Your Highness,
thank you for the warning.

00:01:40.599 --> 00:01:42.560
I will settle this account with her.

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:50.040
The noble lady departs.

00:01:50.319 --> 00:01:53.000
All idlers step aside.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:07.159
Qing Yan.

00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:09.400
Something bad! General
was accused of visiting prostitutes

00:02:09.560 --> 00:02:10.919
and was taken away
by King Of Xiling's men.

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:13.000
King Of Xiling?

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:16.080
Such precise timing.

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:18.719
Empress Dowager
and Princess just left,

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:20.360
and now they come to seize him.

00:02:25.719 --> 00:02:26.759
Just yesterday, General

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:28.919
argued strongly
for you and Princess.

00:02:29.039 --> 00:02:30.639
How could such a thing happen today?

00:02:30.919 --> 00:02:32.319
It must be someone's scheme.

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:34.000
Of course I know

00:02:34.159 --> 00:02:35.439
his feelings for me.

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.159
Your Lordship.

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:40.360
(King Of Xiling)

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:42.599
Your Lordship,
my husband has always been upright.

00:02:42.759 --> 00:02:43.840
Devoted only to military affairs,

00:02:43.919 --> 00:02:45.319
never indulging in debauchery.

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:47.639
Surely there must be a misunderstanding.

00:02:48.719 --> 00:02:50.039
Xiao Yun has great battle merits.

00:02:50.520 --> 00:02:52.879
Who knew that just after
being named Grand General of Cavarly,

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:55.439
he would wallow in place
like Mochun Brothel?

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:57.159
Assaulting courtesans.

00:02:57.439 --> 00:02:58.879
It is grave disrespect to His Majesty.

00:02:59.199 --> 00:03:00.199
Such wicked conduct,

00:03:00.479 --> 00:03:01.759
at the least dismissal,

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:03.639
at the worst, exile.

00:03:04.240 --> 00:03:05.039
Exile?

00:03:06.960 --> 00:03:08.520
General would never
show such disrespect.

00:03:08.599 --> 00:03:10.520
I know all the girls of Mochun Brothel.

00:03:10.719 --> 00:03:13.319
Which lady
did Xiao Yun supposedly offend?

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:14.759
Please tell me, Your Lordship.

00:03:17.599 --> 00:03:19.270
Of course it was
the famous courtesan of Jiangzhou

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:21.039
at Mochun Brothel,

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:24.759
which is you, Lady Qing Yan.

00:03:35.759 --> 00:03:36.479
How could they

00:03:36.479 --> 00:03:37.719
slander General Xiao like this?

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:38.879
This is outrageous!

00:03:39.080 --> 00:03:40.039
They clearly know

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:41.639
you were never of the courtesan class,

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:43.479
yet they still choose to humiliate you.

00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:47.960
Of course I know that too.

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:51.639
General has always been upright.

00:03:51.919 --> 00:03:54.280
Even in the army,
there's little gossip about him.

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:58.080
They're laying a trap.

00:03:58.159 --> 00:03:59.840
Deliberately tainting his honor.

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:01.879
It's more than that.

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:04.759
They want him dead.

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:09.520
No matter.

00:04:10.120 --> 00:04:11.360
I have already found a way.

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:12.280
Tomorrow,

00:04:12.479 --> 00:04:13.919
you two will accompany me to testify.

00:04:14.719 --> 00:04:16.519
Since His Lordship wants this show,

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:18.519
I'll play it to the end.

00:04:20.759 --> 00:04:21.439
Your Lordship.

00:04:21.839 --> 00:04:23.600
My son Ye was exiled to Qiongzhou

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:25.160
some time ago.

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:27.279
In the past, you looked after him much.

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:28.399
Could it be...

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:30.079
Grand Madam.

00:04:30.839 --> 00:04:31.879
His Lordship did not come today

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.079
for that matter.

00:04:33.279 --> 00:04:35.160
Please be patient for now.

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:38.680
What is His Lordship here for?

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:43.360
Qing Yan, what are you doing?

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:45.399
You failing to restrain yourself
is one thing,

00:04:45.720 --> 00:04:47.759
but bringing a courtesan
to ruin the Xiao family?

00:04:48.720 --> 00:04:49.920
Why can't I come?

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:52.720
Is the Xiao Residence gilded with gold?

00:04:52.759 --> 00:04:54.319
More precious than the royal palace?

00:04:54.439 --> 00:04:55.040
You...

00:04:58.279 --> 00:05:00.519
Your Lordship says
I committed adultery with Xiao Yun,

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:01.759
punishable by exile.

00:05:02.319 --> 00:05:03.759
All the women of Mochun Brothel

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:05.079
can testify for me.

00:05:05.800 --> 00:05:06.800
That night the General

00:05:07.040 --> 00:05:09.160
was in my room discussing matters.

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:11.920
He did nothing improper.

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.560
Besides,

00:05:14.560 --> 00:05:16.120
I was never registered as a courtesan.

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:19.040
So how could General be in my room

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:21.360
and seeking the pleasures
of a prostitute?

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:23.360
I beg Your Lordship to see clearly.

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:30.879
It seems Your Lordship
is still unsatisfied.

00:05:31.399 --> 00:05:32.759
With just my word

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.759
truly hard to believe.

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:36.240
However,

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.399
Xiao Yun and I

00:05:39.519 --> 00:05:40.680
have long been close.

00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:42.639
Everyone throughout

00:05:43.240 --> 00:05:44.000
the Xiao Residence

00:05:44.439 --> 00:05:45.920
can testify for me.

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:00.199
Su...

00:06:00.639 --> 00:06:01.759
Su Hua!

00:06:03.600 --> 00:06:04.680
Didn't you already...

00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:08.040
Xiao Yun and I have long
pledged our lives.

00:06:08.639 --> 00:06:10.399
Even if we shared
a man and woman's bond,

00:06:10.600 --> 00:06:11.959
it was only natural

00:06:12.079 --> 00:06:13.160
and born of mutual love.

00:06:14.120 --> 00:06:15.720
How can it be called adultery?

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:20.040
So Ye's words were not nonsense.

00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:22.759
This complicates matters.

00:06:23.079 --> 00:06:24.240
After all,

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:26.279
it's still the word of a courtesan.

00:06:26.759 --> 00:06:27.920
Even if I believe it,

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:31.759
how can the people
of the realm believe it?

00:06:34.759 --> 00:06:35.360
In this matter,

00:06:35.959 --> 00:06:37.560
is there anyone else who can testify?

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:44.360
Your Lordship,
Ye was also there that day.

00:06:44.680 --> 00:06:47.480
Please summon him back from Qiongzhou

00:06:47.959 --> 00:06:49.480
to prove Xiao Yun's innocence.

00:06:49.920 --> 00:06:50.480
You...

00:06:52.879 --> 00:06:55.399
Is what Grand Madam Xiao said true?

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:59.519
Xiao Ye was indeed present that day.

00:07:03.279 --> 00:07:03.800
Go.

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:06.519
Send orders to summon
Xiao Ye back from Qiongzhou.

00:07:06.839 --> 00:07:07.639
Thank you, Your Lordship.

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:08.439
Your Lordship.

00:07:09.399 --> 00:07:12.120
Xiao Ye has always been jealous
of Xiao Yun.

00:07:12.199 --> 00:07:14.680
That day, he was enraged.

00:07:15.519 --> 00:07:16.639
If letting him testify,

00:07:17.920 --> 00:07:18.839
he might frame him.

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:19.839
Insolence!

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:23.920
Are you suggesting His Lordship
is unjust in judgment?

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:27.680
I only fear it might tarnish
Your Lordship's reputation.

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:30.759
I will handle it impartially.

00:07:32.519 --> 00:07:33.920
If Your Lordship wants
to protect Xiao Ye,

00:07:34.680 --> 00:07:36.160
it's only a word away.

00:07:36.600 --> 00:07:38.240
Why go through so much trouble,

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:41.439
drag Mochun Brothel
and yourself into this?

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:44.560
Once Xiao Ye returns,

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:47.360
the Xiao Residence will know no peace.

00:07:48.920 --> 00:07:50.519
If they can slander you like this,

00:07:50.759 --> 00:07:53.079
who knows what schemes they'll use next?

00:07:54.480 --> 00:07:56.079
How could I not worry?

00:07:56.399 --> 00:07:57.519
You've been wronged.

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:01.959
How is it?

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:03.519
Have you found Xiao Ye?

00:08:03.680 --> 00:08:05.319
Will he testify for Xiao Yun?

00:08:06.680 --> 00:08:07.920
We found him.

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:08.680
But...

00:08:09.319 --> 00:08:11.160
Only a corpse was found.

00:08:12.040 --> 00:08:12.839
What do you mean?

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:14.839
It means,

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:17.319
to protect himself, General Xiao

00:08:17.439 --> 00:08:19.399
killed his own brother Xiao Ye.

00:08:19.519 --> 00:08:21.399
Throw him into
the death prison immediately!

00:08:21.900 --> 00:08:24.000
(Xiao Residence)

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:26.519
Is General all right?

00:08:26.759 --> 00:08:27.759
Something happened to him.

00:08:27.759 --> 00:08:28.519
What happened?

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:30.120
Xiao Ye is dead.

00:08:30.130 --> 00:08:31.199
They say the General killed him.

00:08:31.199 --> 00:08:32.080
Dead?

00:08:33.200 --> 00:08:33.799
Su Hua!

00:08:34.159 --> 00:08:34.879
You demon!

00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:35.960
Give me back my son!

00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:37.080
What are you doing?

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:41.360
You ghost! You demon!

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:43.360
Since you came to the Xiao family,

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:45.559
we've had no peace.

00:08:45.919 --> 00:08:48.320
You and Xiao Yun killed Ye!

00:08:48.759 --> 00:08:50.080
Xiao Ye raped women,

00:08:50.879 --> 00:08:52.360
the evidence is undeniable.

00:08:52.519 --> 00:08:54.840
Grand Madam,
not only did you not stop him,

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:56.559
you even handled his aftermath.

00:08:56.919 --> 00:08:57.960
If there's a killer to blame,

00:08:58.320 --> 00:08:59.759
you're one as well.

00:09:05.320 --> 00:09:05.960
Qing Yan.

00:09:10.879 --> 00:09:11.480
Qing Yan.

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.330
I will definitely find out the truth

00:09:21.679 --> 00:09:23.120
about Xiao Ye's death.

00:09:23.639 --> 00:09:25.080
I will never allow you

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:27.159
to tarnish Xiao Yun in the slightest.

00:09:28.279 --> 00:09:29.720
But if I find out

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:31.679
that Xiao Ye is not dead,

00:09:31.960 --> 00:09:34.120
and that this was your scheme
to frame him,

00:09:35.320 --> 00:09:36.279
I will make you

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:39.360
pay a terrible price.

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:07.640
♪Mountains and rivers rise and fall♪

00:10:07.640 --> 00:10:10.840
♪The vast sea opens wide♪

00:10:11.840 --> 00:10:14.840
♪Thank you for staying with me♪

00:10:14.840 --> 00:10:18.920
♪To witness all the lights of the world♪

00:10:19.480 --> 00:10:23.680
♪I remember by the old tree in Qing Yan♪

00:10:24.280 --> 00:10:26.720
♪When we first met♪

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:34.440
♪Looking back, no more words are needed♪

00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:39.320
♪You went left, I went right♪

00:10:39.320 --> 00:10:43.400
♪If we hadn't met,
there'd be nothing to seek♪

00:10:44.080 --> 00:10:47.720
♪In this long, dusty road of life♪

00:10:47.720 --> 00:10:51.320
♪Love and hate poured
in a single jar of wine♪

00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:55.200
♪Whose heart does love truly claim♪

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:59.520
♪Yet it yields to just one greeting♪

00:11:00.360 --> 00:11:03.720
♪Gentle longing flows into the river♪

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:09.520
♪When dreams break,
we will guard each other still♪